creator: DMM SOLUTIONS INC.
descriptionHtml:
Are you looking for the ultimate online dating experience? Get much more than a simple matchmaking service with #1 dating and chat app - Dating.com!

You can watch streams, chat, date and get closer to millions of single women and men from around the world! With the Dating.com streaming, dating and chat app, you can date anyone, anywhere using the best features around. Get the Dating.com app to discover a whole world of singles full of fun, love, life, and energy. This bright and effective chat app quickly and easily lets you chat to the best local and international matches. Use dynamic, real-time features to hit it off with interesting and attractive members!

Meet attractive new people from all walks of life and explore a variety of cultures, cuisines and more. Dating.com offers a large membership of singles from Europe, Australia, America, Asia, and beyond!

Here are the main features of Dating.com:

❤ Browse and meet singles both locally and globally
❤ Enjoy live streams of beautiful singles
❤ Find your best match in just 2 clicks!
❤ Get introduced to singles based on your preferences
❤ Met matches who are serious about dating and relationship
❤ Be protected - 24/7 customer support checks and verifies every member
❤ Talk in real-time and stay in touch at all times with Instant Chat & Offline Messages
❤ Use Video Chat to see your matches live!
❤ Register FREE to chat and date

Do not miss the opportunity to experience global dating in a completely new light and find love in and around your world!

About Us:
Dating.com is at the forefront of the online dating world and offers an unmatched global reach. Launched in 1993, our company now covers more than 32 countries and offers technology that lets members take dating further than ever. Our ambition is to connect singles no matter where they are and inspire romance on a global scale. The experience we have built since our launch has given us a real insight into what people look for when it comes to dating. We offer the most direct and successful approach to meeting singles anywhere in the world.

Dating.com – Always Global:
Dating.com feels at home all over the world. We have headquarters in New York but our global presence means we have offices in Europe, Asia and Latin America. That is because we know the world of romance has changed. Now singles want to search further afield for their special someone. And Dating.com is in the perfect position to introduce matches from a range of places and cultures.

Our Mission:
Everything we do is aimed at bringing singles together and helping them start a relationship with a special person. We have developed this skill into a fine art! Our effective approach helps couples find each other on our website.
That is why we continue to be inspired by the love of those who use Dating.com ❤

Launched in 1993, our company now covers more than 32 countries and offers technology that lets members take dating further than ever. Our ambition is to connect singles no matter where they are and inspire romance on a global scale. The experience we have built since our launch has given us a real insight into what people look for when it comes to dating. We offer the most direct and successful approach to meeting singles anywhere in the world.

Dating.com – Always Global:
Dating.com feels at home all over the world. We have headquarters in New York but our global presence means we have offices in Europe, Asia and Latin America. That is because we know the world of romance has changed. Now singles want to search further afield for their special someone. And Dating.com is in the perfect position to introduce matches from a range of places and cultures.

Our Mission:
Everything we do is aimed at bringing singles together and helping them start a relationship with a special person. We have developed this skill into a fine art! Our effective approach helps couples find each other on our website.
That is why we continue to be inspired by the love of those who use Dating.com ❤

descriptionHtml:

Get the most out of this powerful, must-have online dating app:
🌏 EXPAND YOUR CHOICES
Dating.com lets you connect with lonely women and men. You have so many options to find a date in Europe, America, Australia, Asia, and beyond. Get closer whether you’re traveling or dating online from home!

💘 FIND WHATEVER YOU WANT
Get exactly what you want whether you wish to find a friend, or it’s a serious new relationship, exciting chat, or a mix of everything. And get an acquaintance every way you want with our ample features. Variety is the spice of Dating.com!

😍 DATE SINGLES WITH A DIFFERENCE
Dating.com offers you an unrivalled set of internet dating features big on innovation. We just added the brand new way to date – live stream! Now you can enjoy video dating - watch singles broadcast in real-time and see their personality shine.

💞 EVERY FEATURE YOU’LL NEED
• Register FREE to browse and connect to one of the most popular dating apps.
• Search for a virtual date based on your preferences.
• View stunning profiles and high-quality photos of single girls and guys.
• Get notifications when someone looking for friends messages you.
• Watch live streams of attractive single ladies and men.
✔ Subscribe and get premium features to meet mobile:
• Access private photos & videos.
• Chat in real-time to get closer.
• Use offline messages to stay in touch and talk to new people.
• Video Chat: meet face-to-face.
• Swap photos and build trust while meeting online.
• Send stickers, animated smilies in the dating messenger.
• Try Let’s Mingle and get more interest.

🔒 COMPLETE PEACE OF MIND
We are committed to safe traditional dating, privacy protection and member verification. Our AI-powered screening and moderation system safeguards our community 24/7. You can depend on our online dating service!

♥️ DATING.COM – DEVOTED TO YOU
Dating.com offers you the freedom and flexibility to meet new friends anywhere! Over 25 years of expertise and purpose-driven technology has given us the power to make love happen in new ways. Mobile dating inspires us whether it’s a two-way private chat or a live party stream. That’s why we match millions of members online every day.

IMPORTANT SUBSCRIPTION DETAILS
• Subscribe to chat with other members via this app.
• Choose one of three great subscription packages to use premium features – 150 Credits/month ($29.99 for the 1st month, then $69.99/month); 400 Credits/month ($142.99); and 950 Credits/month ($269.99).
• Your Google Play account will be charged once you confirm your purchase.
• Your subscription will renew automatically unless you cancel within 24-hours prior to the end of your current subscription.
• You can switch off auto-renewal by going to your Google Play account settings after the purchase.

Privacy policy: https://www.dating.com/privacy-policy/

Dating.com is the stylish dating platform that allows you to meet single women and men in over 75 countries. Grab your chance to transform how you date online and meet singles – someone really special. Whether you're seeking a relationship or simply looking to meet people and expand your social circle, our platform offers a seamless experience for everyone looking to connect. Send your life in thrilling new directions…
Get the most out of this powerful, must-have online dating app:

🌏 EXPAND YOUR CHOICES
Dating.com lets you connect with single women and men. You have so many options to find a date in Europe, America, Australia, Asia, and beyond. Get closer whether you’re traveling or dating online from home!

💘 FIND WHATEVER YOU WANT
Match exactly with whom you want whether you wish to find a friend, or it’s a serious new relationship, exciting chat, or a mix of everything. And get an acquaintance every way you want with our ample features. Variety is the spice of Dating.com online dating app!

😍 DATE SINGLES WITH A DIFFERENCE
Dating.com online dating solution offers you an unrivalled set of features big on innovation.

💞 EVERY FEATURE YOU’LL NEED
• Register FREE to browse and connect to one of the most popular dating apps.
• Search for a virtual date based on your preferences.
• View stunning profiles and high-quality photos of singles.
• Get notifications when someone looking for friends messages you.

✔ Subscribe and get premium features to find new friends:
• Access private photos & videos.
• Chat with people online in real-time to get closer.
• Use offline messages to stay in touch and talk to new people.
• Video Chat: meet face-to-face.
• Swap photos and build trust.
• Send stickers, animated smilies.
• Try Let’s Mingle and get more interest.

🔒 COMPLETE PEACE OF MIND
We are committed to safe dating, privacy protection and member verification. Our AI-powered screening and moderation system safeguards our community 24/7. You can depend on our online dating service! Date safely with Dating.com!

♥️ DATING.COM – DEVOTED TO YOU
Dating.com offers you the freedom and flexibility to meet new friends or match and date single people anywhere! Over 25 years of expertise and purpose-driven technology has given us the power to make love happen in new ways. Online dating inspires us, that’s why we match millions of members online every day.
